The paper deals with optimization problems and proposes local search heuristics for the Multidimensional Assignment Problem (MAP), which is a well-known problem in operations research. Therefore, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.OR (Operations Research) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes new neighborhoods and evaluates the heuristics experimentally, which suggests that it may belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with optimization algorithms, which may also make it relevant to cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
